{"word":"ἀνολολύζω","slug":"ἀνολολύζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνολολύζω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to cry aloud, shout (with joy)</i>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to bewail loudly</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in a causal sense, <i>to excite by Bacchic cries</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}